                   </tr></table></div></td></tr></table>                    <table cellspacing=\"0\" id=\"wysija_body\" align=\"center\" style=\"background: none; background-color:#ffffff; border-collapse: collapse; mso-table-lspace:0pt; mso-table-rspace:0pt; border-spacing: 0; margin-bottom: 0; margin-left: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-top: 0; padding-bottom: 0; padding-left: 0; padding-right: 0; padding-top: 0; width: 600px;\" width=\"600\" cellpadding=\"0\"><tr valign=\"top\"><td id=\"wysija_body_content\" style=\"margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;margin-right:0;margin-top:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-left:0;padding-right:0;padding-top:0;width:600px;\" width=\"600\">\n<div style=\"background-color:#ffffff;clear:both; margin-bottom: 0; margin-left: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-top: 0; padding: 0;\">\n    <table style=\"border-collapse: collapse; mso-table-lspace:0pt; mso-table-rspace:0pt; border-spacing: 0; margin: auto;\" width=\"600\">\n        <tr style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\">\n            <td style=\"background-color:#ffffff;clear:both;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;margin-right:0;margin-top:0;padding-top:10px;padding-bottom:10px;padding-left:18px;padding-right:18px;\" width=\"600\">\n                <div style=\"width:564px;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;margin-right:0;margin-top:0;padding:0;\">\n                \n                <h3 style=\"font-family:\'Trebuchet MS\';font-size:24px;color:#424242 !important;border:0;font-weight:normal;line-height:1.1em;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0;padding-top:0;padding-right:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-left:0;word-wrap:break-word;\">We are looking forward to launch V2.0 ...</h3><p style=\"font-family:\'Arial\';font-size:16px;color:#000000 !important;background-color:#ffffff;border:0;line-height:1.5em;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:1em;margin-left:0;padding-top:3px;padding-right:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-left:0;vertical-align:top;word-wrap:break-word;\">You are receiving this email because you installed the Vimbli App. &nbsp;Many of you helped us by providing feedback on the app.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"font-family:\'Arial\';font-size:16px;color:#000000 !important;background-color:#ffffff;border:0;line-height:1.5em;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:1em;margin-left:0;padding-top:3px;padding-right:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-left:0;vertical-align:top;word-wrap:break-word;\">Now we are asking you to help us prepare for the launch of Vimbli 2.0 by updating your subscription information, and by completing the survey \"<a style=\"font-family:\'Arial\';font-size:16px;color:#0000FF !important;background-color:#ffffff;border:0;\" href=\"https://www.surveymonkey.com/s/NewJobSuccess\" title=\"Survey - What Matters Most\" target=\"_blank\">What matters most in the first 90 days.</a>\" &nbsp;You\'ll also get a chance to win a $100 Amazon gift card ...&nbsp;</p>\n                </div>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n    </table>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background-color:#ffffff;clear:both; margin-bottom: 0; margin-left: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-top: 0; padding: 0;\">\n    <table style=\"border-collapse: collapse; mso-table-lspace:0pt; mso-table-rspace:0pt; border-spacing: 0; margin: auto;\" width=\"600\">\n        <tr style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\">\n            <td style=\"background-color:#ffffff;clear:both;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;margin-right:0;margin-top:0;padding-top:10px;padding-bottom:10px;padding-left:18px;padding-right:18px;\" width=\"600\">\n                <div style=\"width:564px;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;margin-right:0;margin-top:0;padding:0;\">\n                \n                    \n                    \n                    \n                    \n                    <div   style=\"width:564px;height:177px;max-height:177px;overflow:hidden;border:0;text-align:center;margin-top:0;margin-right:auto;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:auto;padding-top:0;padding-right:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-left:0;\">\n                        <table align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border:1px solid #ffffff;border-collapse: collapse; mso-table-lspace:0pt; mso-table-rspace:0pt; border-spacing: 0;\">\n                            <tr style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\">\n                                <td style=\"background-color:#ffffff;mso-table-lspace:0;mso-table-rspace:0;clear:both;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;margin-right:0;margin-top:0;padding-top:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-left:0;padding-right:0;\" height=\"177\" width=\"564\" valign=\"top\" align=\"center\">\n                                    \n                                    <img src=\"http://vimbli.com/beta/app/webroot/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/iStock_000021386717Large-0041.jpg\" height=\"177\" alt=\"\" width=\"564\" style=\"border:0;line-height:0.1em;margin:0;padding:0;\" />\n                                    \n                                </td>\n                            </tr>\n                        </table>\n                    </div>\n                \n                \n                </div>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n    </table>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background-color:#ffffff;clear:both; margin-bottom: 0; margin-left: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-top: 0; padding: 0;\">\n    <table style=\"border-collapse: collapse; mso-table-lspace:0pt; mso-table-rspace:0pt; border-spacing: 0; margin: auto;\" width=\"600\">\n        <tr style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\">\n            <td style=\"background-color:#ffffff;clear:both;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;margin-right:0;margin-top:0;padding-top:10px;padding-bottom:10px;padding-left:18px;padding-right:18px;\" width=\"600\">\n                <div style=\"width:564px;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;margin-right:0;margin-top:0;padding:0;\">\n                \n                <p style=\"font-family:\'Arial\';font-size:16px;color:#000000 !important;background-color:#ffffff;border:0;line-height:1.5em;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:1em;margin-left:0;padding-top:3px;padding-right:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-left:0;vertical-align:top;word-wrap:break-word;\"><span>We had people from more than 20 countries using our Android App. You were one of them! &nbsp;Thank you.</span></p><p style=\"font-family:\'Arial\';font-size:16px;color:#000000 !important;background-color:#ffffff;border:0;line-height:1.5em;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:1em;margin-left:0;padding-top:3px;padding-right:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-left:0;vertical-align:top;word-wrap:break-word;\"><span>We received valuable input and are busy putting the finishing touches on a small number of commercial pilots using Vimbli V2.0.</span></p><p style=\"font-family:\'Arial\';font-size:16px;color:#000000 !important;background-color:#ffffff;border:0;line-height:1.5em;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:1em;margin-left:0;padding-top:3px;padding-right:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-left:0;vertical-align:top;word-wrap:break-word;\"><span>V2 is a business solution for corporate&nbsp;onboarding. The aim: Improve the performance and experience of new hires in the corporate context. &nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"font-family:\'Arial\';font-size:16px;color:#000000 !important;background-color:#ffffff;border:0;line-height:1.5em;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:1em;margin-left:0;padding-top:3px;padding-right:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-left:0;vertical-align:top;word-wrap:break-word;\"><span>V2 uses integration with calendar and address book, and we are adding email. &nbsp;All in the Google environment. We are also adding more comprehensive goals setting and accountability features. &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"font-family:\'Arial\';font-size:16px;color:#000000 !important;background-color:#ffffff;border:0;line-height:1.5em;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:1em;margin-left:0;padding-top:3px;padding-right:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-left:0;vertical-align:top;word-wrap:break-word;\"><span>At the moment, Vimbli is still available in Google Play, but we are focusing all of our resources on V2. We don\'t expect any updates to&nbsp;V1.</span></p><p style=\"font-family:\'Arial\';font-size:16px;color:#000000 !important;background-color:#ffffff;border:0;line-height:1.5em;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:1em;margin-left:0;padding-top:3px;padding-right:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-left:0;vertical-align:top;word-wrap:break-word;\"><span>While we get ready to release V2, you can help! Please:</span></p><p style=\"font-family:\'Arial\';font-size:16px;color:#000000 !important;background-color:#ffffff;border:0;line-height:1.5em;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:1em;margin-left:0;padding-top:3px;padding-right:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-left:0;vertical-align:top;word-wrap:break-word;\"><span>1. &nbsp;Update your contact details by using one of the links below.</span></p><p style=\"font-family:\'Arial\';font-size:16px;color:#000000 !important;background-color:#ffffff;border:0;line-height:1.5em;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:1em;margin-left:0;padding-top:3px;padding-right:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-left:0;vertical-align:top;word-wrap:break-word;\"><span>2. &nbsp;Complete a&nbsp;<a style=\"font-family:\'Arial\';font-size:16px;color:#0000FF !important;background-color:#ffffff;border:0;\" href=\"https://www.surveymonkey.com/s/NewJobSuccess\" title=\"What Matters Most\" target=\"_blank\">survey</a><span>&nbsp;</span>on what matters when you start in a new role (<a style=\"font-family:\'Arial\';font-size:16px;color:#0000FF !important;background-color:#ffffff;border:0;\" href=\"https://www.surveymonkey.com/s/NewJobSuccess\">You have a chance to win $100</a>). &nbsp;Please forward to others as well. &nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"font-family:\'Arial\';font-size:16px;color:#000000 !important;background-color:#ffffff;border:0;line-height:1.5em;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:1em;margin-left:0;padding-top:3px;padding-right:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-left:0;vertical-align:top;word-wrap:break-word;\"