;padding-bottom:0;padding-left:0;vertical-align:top;word-wrap:break-word;\"><span>You are receiving this email because you are a personal or professional friend.&nbsp;</span><span>I am asking you to help me get Vimbli ready for the formal launch later in 2013. &nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"font-family:\'Arial\';font-size:16px;color:#000000 !important;background-color:#ffffff;border:0;line-height:1.5em;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:1em;margin-left:0;padding-top:3px;padding-right:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-left:0;vertical-align:top;word-wrap:break-word;\"><span>We had people from more than 20 countries using the Android App! &nbsp;The prototype helped us better define the Vimbli value proposition and resulted in Vimbli 2.0.</span></p><p style=\"font-family:\'Arial\';font-size:16px;color:#000000 !important;background-color:#ffffff;border:0;line-height:1.5em;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:1em;margin-left:0;padding-top:3px;padding-right:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-left:0;vertical-align:top;word-wrap:break-word;\"><span>V2 is a strategic onboarding solution (</span><a style=\"font-family:\'Arial\';font-size:16px;color:#0000FF !important;background-color:#ffffff;border:0;\" href=\"http://vimbli.com/beta/pages/why_sos\" title=\"More on SOS\" target=\"_blank\">SOS</a><span>) designed to improve the performance and experience of new hires. &nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"font-family:\'Arial\';font-size:16px;color:#000000 !important;background-color:#ffffff;border:0;line-height:1.5em;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:1em;margin-left:0;padding-top:3px;padding-right:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-left:0;vertical-align:top;word-wrap:break-word;\">We currently have a limited number of individual testers, and are working towards 3-4 pilots with larger groups. We hope to be adding more individual users in the next few weeks. &nbsp;</p><p style=\"font-family:\'Arial\';font-size:16px;color:#000000 !important;background-color:#ffffff;border:0;line-height:1.5em;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:1em;margin-left:0;padding-top:3px;padding-right:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-left:0;vertical-align:top;word-wrap:break-word;\">How can you help? You can help by doing any (or all of the things below).</p><p style=\"font-family:\'Arial\';font-size:16px;color:#000000 !important;background-color:#ffffff;border:0;line-height:1.5em;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:1em;margin-left:0;padding-top:3px;padding-right:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-left:0;vertical-align:top;word-wrap:break-word;\"><strong>1. Update</strong>&nbsp;your subscription information using the links below. (I have added you to the mailing list, we\'ll send out weekly emails from now going forward. I will not feel bad if you unsubscribe, but it will be an honor to have you on the list.)</p><p style=\"font-family:\'Arial\';font-size:16px;color:#000000 !important;background-color:#ffffff;border:0;line-height:1.5em;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:1em;margin-left:0;padding-top:3px;padding-right:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-left:0;vertical-align:top;word-wrap:break-word;\"><strong>2. Complete</strong>&nbsp;the survey \"<a style=\"font-family:\'Arial\';font-size:16px;color:#0000FF !important;background-color:#ffffff;border:0;\" href=\"https://www.surveymonkey.com/s/NewJobSuccess\" title=\"Survey - What Matters Most\" target=\"_blank\">What matters most in the first 90 days</a>\" if you have made a role or career change in the past 36 months.&nbsp;You\'ll also get a chance to win a $100 Amazon gift card ... (The survey takes less than 10 minutes to complete, and your response will make a difference. If you can complete the survey and recruit three others to complete the survey, we\'ll get to our response goal!)</p><p style=\"font-family:\'Arial\';font-size:16px;color:#000000 !important;background-color:#ffffff;border:0;line-height:1.5em;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:1em;margin-left:0;padding-top:3px;padding-right:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-left:0;verti