ght:1.5em;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:1em;margin-left:0;padding-top:3px;padding-right:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-left:0;vertical-align:top;word-wrap:break-word;\"><strong>2. Complete</strong>&nbsp;the survey \"<a style=\"font-family:\'Arial\';font-size:16px;color:#0000FF !important;background-color:#ffffff;border:0;\" href=\"https://www.surveymonkey.com/s/NewJobSuccess\" title=\"Survey - What Matters Most\" target=\"_blank\">What matters most in the first 90 days</a>\" if you have made a role or career change in the past 36 months.&nbsp;You\'ll also get a chance to win a $100 Amazon gift card ... (The survey takes less than 10 minutes to complete, and your response will make a difference. If you can complete the survey and recruit three others to complete the survey, we\'ll get to our response goal!)</p><p style=\"font-family:\'Arial\';font-size:16px;color:#000000 !important;background-color:#ffffff;border:0;line-height:1.5em;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:1em;margin-left:0;padding-top:3px;padding-right:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-left:0;vertical-align:top;word-wrap:break-word;\"><strong>3. Let me know</strong>&nbsp;if you or your company are interested in being a pilot client.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"font-family:\'Arial\';font-size:16px;color:#000000 !important;background-color:#ffffff;border:0;line-height:1.5em;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:1em;margin-left:0;padding-top:3px;padding-right:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-left:0;vertical-align:top;word-wrap:break-word;\">Your help in getting Vimbli off the ground is much appreciated. Without your ongoing support it will be much less rewarding to build Vimbli.</p><p style=\"font-family:\'Arial\';font-size:16px;color:#000000 !important;background-color:#ffffff;border:0;line-height:1.5em;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:1em;margin-left:0;padding-top:3px;padding-right:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-left:0;vertical-align:top;word-wrap:break-word;\">Thanks in advance!</p><p style=\"font-fami